WEBVTT

1
00:24:34.060 --> 00:24:38.280 
却把她健健康康的孩子扔下桥
throws her perfectly healthy kids off of a bridge.

2
00:24:38.290 --> 00:24:40.390 
你难道不火大吗
Doesn't that just enrage you?

3
00:24:40.390 --> 00:24:41.240 
-艾普丽尔  -我想说
- April... - I'm saying...

4
00:24:41.540 --> 00:24:45.190 
她做出这样的事  你怎么能忍得住不发飙
How are you not screaming right now at what she's done?

5
00:24:45.190 --> 00:24:47.370 
伤害了她的孩子  伤害了这么多无辜的人
To her kids? To all of these people?!

6
00:24:47.620 --> 00:24:49.840 
这根本就不公平
How is any of this fair?!

7
00:24:49.840 --> 00:24:51.240 
艾普丽尔  冷静
April! April.

8
00:24:51.710 --> 00:24:52.940 
艾普丽尔
April.

9
00:24:53.410 --> 00:24:54.090 
好的
Okay.

10
00:24:54.190 --> 00:24:54.690 
现在
Now --

11
00:24:54.690 --> 00:24:55.960 
病人们还在等着
Patients are waiting.

12
00:25:02.270 --> 00:25:05.450 
我女儿的脸上会留下疤痕吗
Will my daughter have a scar for the rest of her life?

